text_occasion_en(111,'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;With the Vienna Culture Alderman, Dr. Helmut Zilk, acting as a go-between, Hundertwasser was invited by the Directors of the IGA &rsquo;83 in Munich to propose a poster design and submit one of his ideas for a more human architecture in harmony with nature. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the &lt;em&gt;Westpark&lt;/em&gt; were realised the architecture model HIGH-RISE MEADOW HOUSE on a scale of 1:20.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;On the occasion of IGA Hundertwasser wrote the text &ldquo;Concrete Utopias for the Green City&rdquo; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;and installed tree-tenants in Ganghoferstra&szlig;e 86.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;').
text_occasion_en(112,'').
text_occasion_en(113,'').
