text_occasion_ge(114,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Geschrieben 1975/1983.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser sprach mit Pierre Restany im Februar 1975 in Wien &uuml;ber die &raquo;Linie von Hamburg&laquo;, eine Aktion, die 1959 an der Hamburger Kunsthochschule gemeinsam mit Bazon Brock und Herbert Schuldt durchgef&uuml;hrt wurde.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;&nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;').
text_occasion_ge(115,'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;speech in the nude for the right to a third skin in Galerie Hartmann, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Munich&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;December 12, 1967&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;(As p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;art &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;of an initiative by the Pintorarium, a universal academy of all creative pursuits, founded by Hundertwasser, Arnulf Rainer and Ernst Fuchs in 1959, Hundertwasser condemned the enslavement of humans by the sterile gird system of conventional architecture and by the series production of mechanised industries.) &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;').
