text_published_en(103,'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;A signed and numbered brochure, edited by Galerie Renate Boukes: Wiesbaden (Germany), 1958 (German)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Conrads, Ulrich (ed.): Programme und Manifeste zur Architektur des 20. Jahrhunderts. (Programmes and manifestos on architecture of the 20. century) Vieweg Verlag: Berlin, 1964, pp. 149-152 (German)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Published in French in &ldquo;La Nouvelle Revue Fran&ccedil;aise&rdquo; as &ldquo;Manifeste Moisissure&rdquo;, Paris on April 1, 1961, pp. 660-668&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Ullstein Bauwelt Fundamente 1. G&uuml;tersloh, 1964 (German)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Breicha, Otto (ed.): Aufforderungen zum Mi&szlig;trauen. (Demand for Distrust) Residenz Verlag: Salzburg, 1967 (German)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Published in English in the Hundertwasser exhibition catalogue by Herschel B. Chipp and Brenda Richardsons for the University of California, Berkeley, 1968, pp. 94-104&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Berkeley Students Magazine 1968&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s private print with manifestos and speeches in the nude in 1967 and 1968. Vienna, 2&lt;sup&gt;nd&lt;/sup&gt; edition, 1968 (German)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Exhibition catalogue for Haus de